{"data":[{"name":"93:1","price":"कस़म है धूप चढ़ने के समय की!","arabic":"وَٱلضُّحَىٰ","category":["93 (Ad-Duha)","Ad-Duha","Surah Ad-Duha"],"ayahNumber":6080,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"wal-ḍuḥā ","translations":["By the morning brightness","(1)"],"transliterationArr":["wal-ḍuḥā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1275]]}},{"name":"93:2","price":"और क़सम है रात की, जब वह छा जाए।","arabic":"وَٱلَّيۡلِ إِذَا سَجَىٰ","category":["93 (Ad-Duha)","Ad-Duha","Surah Ad-Duha"],"ayahNumber":6081,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-al-layli idhā sajā ","translations":["And the night","when","it covers with darkness","(2)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-al-layli","idhā","sajā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1090],[2,1090,1680],[3,1680,2545]]}},{"name":"93:3","price":"(ऐ नबी!) तेरे पालनहार ने तुझे न तो छोड़ा और न नाराज़ हुआ।","arabic":"مَا وَدَّعَكَ رَبُّكَ وَمَا قَلَىٰ","category":["93 (Ad-Duha)","Ad-Duha","Surah Ad-Duha"],"ayahNumber":6082,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"mā waddaʿaka rabbuka wamā qalā ","translations":["Not","has forsaken you","your Lord","and not","He is displeased","(3)"],"transliterationArr":["mā","waddaʿaka","rabbuka","wamā","qalā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,490],[2,490,1650],[3,1650,2520],[4,2520,3050],[5,3050,3905]]}},{"name":"93:4","price":"और निश्चित रूप से आख़िरत आपके लिए दुनिया से बेहतर है।","arabic":"وَلَلۡأٓخِرَةُ خَيۡرٞ لَّكَ مِنَ ٱلۡأُولَىٰ","category":["93 (Ad-Duha)","Ad-Duha","Surah Ad-Duha"],"ayahNumber":6083,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"walalākhiratu khayrun laka mina al-ūlā ","translations":["And surely the Hereafter","(is) better","for you","than","the first","(4)"],"transliterationArr":["walalākhiratu","khayrun","laka","mina","al-ūlā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1770],[2,1770,2550],[3,2550,3090],[4,3090,3480],[5,3480,4715]]}},{"name":"93:5","price":"और निश्चय तेरा पालनहार तुझे प्रदान करेगा, तो तू प्रसन्न हो जाएगा।","arabic":"وَلَسَوۡفَ يُعۡطِيكَ رَبُّكَ فَتَرۡضَىٰٓ","category":["93 (Ad-Duha)","Ad-Duha","Surah Ad-Duha"],"ayahNumber":6084,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"walasawfa yuʿ'ṭīka rabbuka fatarḍā ","translations":["And soon","will give you","your Lord","then you will be satisfied","(5)"],"transliterationArr":["walasawfa","yuʿ'ṭīka","rabbuka","fatarḍā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1140],[2,1140,2270],[3,2270,3170],[4,3170,4475]]}},{"name":"93:6","price":"क्या उसने आपको अनाथ पाकर शरण नहीं दी?","arabic":"أَلَمۡ يَجِدۡكَ يَتِيمٗا فَـَٔاوَىٰ","category":["93 (Ad-Duha)","Ad-Duha","Surah Ad-Duha"],"ayahNumber":6085,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"alam yajid'ka yatīman faāwā ","translations":["Did not","He find you","an orphan","and give shelter","(6)"],"transliterationArr":["alam","yajid'ka","yatīman","faāwā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,640],[2,640,1480],[3,1480,3430],[4,3430,4685]]}},{"name":"93:7","price":"और आपको मार्ग से अनभिज्ञ पाया, तो सीधा मार्ग दिखाया।","arabic":"وَوَجَدَكَ ضَآلّٗا فَهَدَىٰ","category":["93 (Ad-Duha)","Ad-Duha","Surah Ad-Duha"],"ayahNumber":6086,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"wawajadaka ḍāllan fahadā ","translations":["And He found you","lost","so He guided","(7)"],"transliterationArr":["wawajadaka","ḍāllan","fahadā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1130],[2,1130,5499],[3,5499,6614]]}},{"name":"93:8","price":"और उसने आपको निर्धन पाया, तो संपन्न कर दिया।","arabic":"وَوَجَدَكَ عَآئِلٗا فَأَغۡنَىٰ","category":["93 (Ad-Duha)","Ad-Duha","Surah Ad-Duha"],"ayahNumber":6087,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"wawajadaka ʿāilan fa-aghnā ","translations":["And He found you","in need","so He made self-sufficient","(8)"],"transliterationArr":["wawajadaka","ʿāilan","fa-aghnā",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1120],[2,1120,4210],[3,4210,5435]]}},{"name":"93:9","price":"अतः आप अनाथ पर कठोरता न दिखाएँ।[1]","arabic":"فَأَمَّا ٱلۡيَتِيمَ فَلَا تَقۡهَرۡ","category":["93 (Ad-Duha)","Ad-Duha","Surah Ad-Duha"],"ayahNumber":6088,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"1. (1-9) इन आयतों में अल्लाह ने नबी सल्लल्लाहु अलैहि व सल्लम से फरमाया है कि तुम्हें यह चिंता कैसे हो गई है कि हम अप्रसन्न हो गए? हमने तो तुम्हारे जन्म के दिन से निरंतर तुमपर उपकार किए हैं। तुम अनाथ थे, तो तुम्हारे पालन और रक्षा की व्यवस्था की। राह से अंजान थे, तो राह दिखाई। निर्धन थे, तो धनी बना दिया। ये बातें बता रही हैं कि तुम आरंभ ही से हमारे प्रियवर हो और तुमपर हमारा उपकार निरंतर रहा है।","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"fa-ammā al-yatīma falā taqhar ","translations":["So as for","the orphan","then (do) not","oppress","(9)"],"transliterationArr":["fa-ammā","al-yatīma","falā","taqhar",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1640],[2,1640,2700],[3,2700,3450],[4,3450,4835]]}},{"name":"93:10","price":"और माँगने वाले को न झिड़कें।","arabic":"وَأَمَّا ٱلسَّآئِلَ فَلَا تَنۡهَرۡ","category":["93 (Ad-Duha)","Ad-Duha","Surah Ad-Duha"],"ayahNumber":6089,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-ammā al-sāila falā tanhar ","translations":["And as for","one who asks","then (do) not","repel","(10)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-ammā","al-sāila","falā","tanhar",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1340],[2,1340,4270],[3,4270,4870],[4,4870,6185]]}},{"name":"93:11","price":"और अपने रब के उपकार का वर्णन करते रहें।[2]","arabic":"وَأَمَّا بِنِعۡمَةِ رَبِّكَ فَحَدِّثۡ","category":["93 (Ad-Duha)","Ad-Duha","Surah Ad-Duha"],"ayahNumber":6090,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"2. (10-11) इन अंतिम आयतों में नबी सल्लल्लाहु अलैहि व सल्लम को बताया गया है कि हमने तुमपर जो उपकार किए हैं, उनके बदले में तुम अल्लाह की उत्पत्ति के साथ दया और उपकार करो यही हमारे उपकारों की कृतज्ञता होगी।","lang":"hi","meta":{"transliteration":"wa-ammā biniʿ'mati rabbika faḥaddith ","translations":["But as for","(the) Favor","(of) your Lord","narrate","(11)"],"transliterationArr":["wa-ammā","biniʿ'mati","rabbika","faḥaddith",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1760],[2,1760,2850],[3,2850,3780],[4,3780,5065]]}}],"chapter":["93 (Ad-Duha)","Ad-Duha","Surah Ad-Duha","Chapter Ad-Duha","Duha","Surah Duha","Chapter Duha","Ad Duha","Surah Ad Duha","Chapter Ad Duha","Surah 93","Chapter 93","The Morning Hours","الضحى"],"version":{"key":"hindi_omari","direction":"ltr","language_iso_code":"hi","version":"1.1.4","last_update":1675069101,"title":"Hindi Translation","description":"Translation of the Quran meanings into Indian by Azizul-Haqq Al-Umary."}}